      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm starting a new project with an NGO in Nigeria soon and wanted to get a quick sense of things. Can you give me a rundown of the main social tensions there right now? Like, how do the different ethnic groups usually interact and what are the main friction points? thanks.",
